---
---
<section class="section patents-section" id="patents">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="patents-wrapper reveal">
      <div class="patents-info">
        <div class="glow-badge">INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY</div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Global <span class="text-gradient">Patents & IP</span></h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">Each piece of intellectual property contributes toward building affordable gold standards in neurocare — without compromising quality or technology.</p>

        <div class="ip-stats">
          <div class="ip-stat">
            <span class="ip-num">15+</span>
            <span class="ip-label">Trademarks</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ip-divider"></div>
          <div class="ip-stat">
            <span class="ip-num">2</span>
            <span class="ip-label">Granted Patents</span>
          </div>
          <div class="ip-divider"></div>
          <div class="ip-stat">
            <span class="ip-num">15+</span>
            <span class="ip-label">Patents Pending</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="patents-mission">
          This IP portfolio reflects the mission to make a <strong>fundamental difference in functional neuroscience</strong> — not just in labs and journals, but at the bedside.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="patents-grid">
        <div class="patent-card">
          <div class="patent-id">NO. 201941038618</div>
          <h4 class="patent-name">Advanced Neuro Rehabilitation Curriculum</h4>
          <p class="patent-meta">A Novel and Robust Framework for clinical excellence in neurorehabilitation.</p>
          <span class="patent-status granted">✓ Granted</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="patent-card">
          <div class="patent-id">NO. 202241067553</div>
          <h4 class="patent-name">Assessment of Functional Brain Circuits</h4>
          <p class="patent-meta">System and Methodology for predicting independence and functional recovery.</p>
          <span class="patent-status granted">✓ Granted</span>
        </div>

        <div class="patent-card">
          <div class="patent-id">NO. 202441038844</div>
          <h4 class="patent-name">Intelligent Rehab Environment</h4>
          <p class="patent-meta">Advancing Functional Neurosciences with IoMT technology integration.</p>
          <span class="patent-status pending">⏳ Pending</span>
        </div>

        <div class="patent-card">
          <div class="patent-id">NO. 202441038858</div>
          <h4 class="patent-name">Multidimensional Prognostic Modelling</h4>
          <p class="patent-meta">Optimizing Functional Neurosciences outcomes through data-driven models.</p>
          <span class="patent-status pending">⏳ Pending</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .patents-section {
    background: #ffffff;
  }

  .glow-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 6px 20px;
    background: rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.1);
    color: var(--primary-color);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    border-radius: 100px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }

  .patents-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 0.9fr 1.1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 36px;
  }

  .ip-stats {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    padding: 24px;
    background: var(--bg-slate);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid rgba(79,70,229,0.08);
  }

  .ip-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .ip-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    background: var(--premium-gradient);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
    line-height: 1;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .ip-label {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .ip-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 40px;
    background: rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .patents-mission {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .patents-mission strong { color: var(--text-main); }

  .patents-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .patent-card {
    background: var(--bg-slate);
    padding: 28px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    transition: var(--transition-smooth);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .patent-card:hover {
    background: white;
    border-color: var(--primary-color);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    transform: translateY(-6px);
  }

  .patent-id {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .patent-name {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-main);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .patent-meta {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
    line-height: 1.5;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .patent-status {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 100px;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-top: 4px;
    align-self: flex-start;
  }

  .patent-status.granted {
    background: rgba(16,185,129,0.1);
    color: #059669;
    border: 1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.25);
  }

  .patent-status.pending {
    background: rgba(245,158,11,0.1);
    color: #d97706;
    border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.25);
  }

  @media (max-width: 1100px) {
    .section-title { font-size: 2.4rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .patents-wrapper {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .patents-info { text-align: center; }
    .ip-stats { justify-content: center; }
    .patents-mission { text-align: left; }
    .section-subtitle { text-align: left; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-title { font-size: 2rem; }
    .patents-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .ip-stats { flex-direction: column; gap: 16px; }
    .ip-divider { width: 60px; height: 1px; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .section-title { font-size: 1.75rem; }
    .patent-card { padding: 20px; }
    .ip-num { font-size: 1.6rem; }
  }
</style>
